attles annoying.\n\nYou can challenge every aspect from the beginning. You can start from anywhere, in any order.\nin any order.\n\nNote that there is some jumping action and falling from heights, so be careful if you are not good at heights or if you get easily intoxicated.\n\nCompatible with MetaQuest Series(Quest/Quest2/Quest3...)\nSitting play is recommended.\nCurrently only available in Japanese and English.\n\nFree trial version is available.\nhttps://www.meta.com/ja-jp/experiences/5562387927144863/\n", "short_description": "A virtual reality giant maze experience to find and reach the goal in the distant future, on a Jupiter that has changed in many ways.\n\nCompatible with Quest/Quest2\nSeated play is recommended.\n\nCurrently only available in Japanese and English.\n\nFree trial version available\nhttps://www.meta.com/ja-jp/experiences/5562387927144863/\n\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://doga.jp/~moriyama/rouKANlien/DownLoadContents/OculusQuest/pckj/pp.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VSC/S.Moriyama", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://doga.jp/~moriyama/rouKANlien/DownLoadContents/OculusQuest/pckj/pckj.html", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["TRAVEL", "ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["ja", "en_US"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8529481787085078"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_squa